OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAfternoon
OL,6,Fsunny spells will persist with the odd
OL,7,Flight spot of rain possible this
OL,8,Fevening. Overnight, clear spells and
OL,9,Flight winds will allow for a rural
OL,10,Ffrost to develop in prone spots.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FDry and bright to start, with
OL,13,Fpatchy cloud developing and the chance
OL,14,Fof an isolated shower at times through
OL,15,Fthe afternoon. A gentle easterly
OL,16,Fbreeze will develop.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
